com.intel.icecp.node.channels.ndn

Class MessageRequestHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intel.icecp.node.channels.ndn.MessageRequestHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.named_data.jndn.OnInterestCallback

    public class MessageRequestHandler
extends Object
implements net.named_data.jndn.OnInterestCallback
    Handler for responding to requests for messages on a channel; this handler expects messages in the form:
    • /channel/name/[marker][message id]
    • /channel/name with rightmost selector
    • /channel/name with leftmost selector
